      News story
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Home Secretary visits the police hubs leading Brexit preparations
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Home Secretary Priti Patel received a briefing today on how police forces will coordinate operations ahead of Brexit.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
